   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The LUFP7 gateway is identified on the Profibus-DP bus by its address
(1–99). The address depends on the position of the two coding
wheels. The first wheel represents the units (0–9), the second
wheel represents the tens (0–90).</p>
